ylistic choices, and how attention to poetic style can aid in literary analysis.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 4aAltenglisch. 4aHypermetrisch. 4aMetrik. 4aMündliche Theorie. 4aStil. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Medieval.2bisacsh  aComparative Metrics.  aHypermetric.  aOld English.  aOral Theory.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package 2020z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package English 2020z978311069628808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter English eBooks 2020 - UCz978311065906108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2020 Englishz978311070474708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2020z9783110704532oZDB-23-DKU0 cEPUBz97815015135580 cprintz978150151832440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150151368840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501513688423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781501513688.jpg  a978-3-11-065906-1  De Gruyter English eBooks 2020 - UCb2020  a978-3-11-069627-1  DG Ebook Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-069628-8  DG Ebook Package English 2020b2020  a978-3-11-070471-6  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-070474-7  EBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2020 Englishb2020  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  aZDB-23-DKUb2020